  "content": " <div class=\"photo top\" style=\"text-align:center\"> <a href=\"https://cmsphoto.ww-cdn.com/superstatic/2009698/art/grande/81108747-58476827.jpg?v=1718913888\" target=\"_blank\"> <img id=\"img-81108747-58476827\" src=\"https://cmsphoto.ww-cdn.com/superstatic/2009698/art/default/81108747-58476827.jpg?v=1718913889\" alt=\"Como fazer as Napkin Presentations\" title=\"Como fazer as Napkin Presentations\" /> </a> </div> <br class=\"clear\" /> <div class=\"texte\" > <p>Foi Albert Einstein quem disse: \"<strong>If you can't explain it simply, you don't understand it well enough.</strong>\" esse é o exato conceito por trás dos napkin presentations. Com esses simples desenhos você consegue entender (e explicar) conceitos financeiros de forma fácil e direta.</p> <p>Estude, pratique, utilize os napkin presentations para ter sucesso na profissão.</p> </div> <br class=\"clear\" /> <div class=\"texte\" > <p><strong>Os 3 ingredientes para criar riqueza:</strong></p> <p>&nbsp;</p> </div> <br class=\"clear\" /> <iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/426544836\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allowfullscreen></iframe> <div class=\"texte\" > <p><strong>O jogo da velha financeiro (Tic-Tac-Dough)</strong></p> </div> <br class=\"clear\" /> <iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/426544985\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allowfullscreen></iframe> <div class=\"texte\" > <p><strong>Bob e o benefício em vida</strong></p> </div> <br class=\"clear\" /> <iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/426573125\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allowfullscreen></iframe> <div class=\"texte\" > <p><strong>O Plano Indexado (sobe e desce da bolsa e carência)</strong></p> </div> <br class=\"clear\" /> <iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/425271415\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allow